        // All `d[i] == pivot` for `i < k` must be 1.
        // All `d[i] == pivot` for `i >= k` must be 2.
        // If no `d[i] == pivot` is colored 2, then all `d[i] == pivot` are 1.
        // If no `d[i] == pivot` is colored 1, then all `d[i] == pivot` are 2.

